{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p01|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 01]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p02|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 02]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p03|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 03]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p04|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 04]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p05|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 05]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p06|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 06]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|narration2|p07|text', 'text' : '[paragraph 07]'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Synaxarion|lastline|text', 'text' : 'By the coming of Your Holy Spirit, by the intercessions of Your Apostles, O Christ God, have mercy on us. Amen.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Kontakion1|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Kontakion1|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Kontakion1|text', 'text' : 'When the Most High God came down and confused the tongues, * He divided the nations. * When He distributed the tongues of fire, * He called all to unity. * And with one voice we glorify the all-holy Spirit.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Oikos1|text', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Exaposteilarion1|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Exaposteilarion1|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Exaposteilarion1|text', 'text' : 'O all-holy Spirit * who from the Father issues forth, * and through the Son was indwelling * in the unlettered Disciples, * sanctify all who acknowledge * You to be God, and save us.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Exaposteilarion2|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Exaposteilarion2|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Exaposteilarion2|text', 'text' : 'Light is the Father, light the Logos; * light is the Holy Spirit, * which was sent to the Apostles * in the form of fiery tongues, * and through which the entire world is guided by the light * to worship the Holy Trinity.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds1|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds1|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds1|text', 'text' : 'In the Prophets You announced to us the way of salvation; and now the grace of Your Spirit has shined in Your Apostles, our Savior. You are God, the first and the last; and to the ages You are our God.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds2|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds2|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds2|text', 'text' : 'In Your courts, I will sing praise to You, the Savior of the world; and on bended knee I will worship Your invincible power. And I will bless You, O Lord, in the evening and the morning, in the middle of the day, and at every time.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds3|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds3|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|Lauds3|text', 'text' : 'In Your courts, O Lord, we the faithful bend the knee of soul and body, and we extol You, the unoriginate Father, and the Son who is also without beginning, and the co-eternal and all-holy Spirit, which illumines and sanctifies our souls.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|LaudsGlory|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|LaudsGlory|melody', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peMA|LaudsGlory|text', 'text' : 'Tongues were confused once because people dared to build the Tower. Tongues now obtain skill, for the glory of divine knowledge. There, God condemned the impious for their transgression; here, by the Spirit, Christ illumined the fishermen. Then, discord was contrived as penalization; now a new concord has arrived, for the salvation of our souls.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peLI|Antiphon2|text', 'text' : 'Save us, O good Comforter.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peLI|MM|EntranceHymn|text', 'text' : 'For media only.'}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peLI|TheotokosHymn|mode', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peLI|TheotokosHymn|text', 'text' : ''}
{'id_' : 'pe|d121_en_US_dedes|peLI|CommunionHymn|text', 'text' : 'Do not take Your Holy Spirit from us, we pray, O Lover of mankind.'}
